1. How do I sync the database?
pacman --sync --refresh
2. How do I search for Git?
pacman --sync --refresh
pacman --syn --search git
3. How do I install Git?
pacman --sync git
( Installs run-parts, ca-cerfificates, curl, perl-error, git )
4. Is there a meta-package for development?
pacman --sync base-devel
